## [0.0.16] - 2018-12-04
### Added
- Support Timeline without groups [#34](https://github.com/alexcode/vue2vis/pull/34).
- Added CHANGELOG.md

### Fixed
- Fix lint errors

### Changed
- Update packages in both lib and examples
